==English==
===Pronunciation===
*[[IPA]]: /ˌho.mi.ˈɑ.pə.θi/
*Other 1: (hōʺmēŏʹpu̇thē)
*Other 2: hoh-mee-AH-puh-thee
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''homeopathy''' (''plural'' '''homeopathies''')
# {{medicine}} a [[system]] of [[treating]] [[disease]]s with small amounts of [[substance]]s which, in larger amounts, would produce the [[observed]] [[symptom]]s.

